  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Quality and safety of human blood and blood products if there's a no-deal Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    What blood establishments, blood banks and manufacturers of blood products need to do to ensure the safety and quality of blood and blood products.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

